祖先元素的**内容框**组成\r\n3. 如果元素`position`为`fixed`。对于连续媒体，它的包含块为 viewport；对于 paged media，包含块为 page area\r\n4. 如果元素`position`为`absolute`，它的包含块由祖先元素中最近一个`position`为`relative`,`absolute`或者`fixed`的元素产生，规则如下：\r\n\r\n   - 如果祖先元素为行内元素，the containing block is the bounding box around the **padding boxes** of the first and the last inline boxes generated for that element.\r\n   - 其他情况下包含块由祖先节点的**padding edge**组成\r\n\r\n   如果找不到定位的祖先元素，包含块为**初始包含块**","closed_by":null,"reactions":{"url":"https://api.github.com/repos/hankliu62/interview/issues/55/reactions","total_count":0,"+1":0,"-1":0,"laugh":0,"hooray":0,"confused":0,"heart":0,"rocket":0,"eyes":0},"timeline_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/hankliu62/interview/issues/55/timeline","performed_via_github_app":null,"state_reason":null},"menus":[]},"__N_SSG":true}